    " **Customer Lifecycle Effect (Tenure)**\n",
    "- New customers show significantly higher churn rates  \n",
    "- Churn risk decreases as customer tenure increases  \n",
    "- This indicates a critical “early-stage risk window”\n",
    "\n",
    " **Pricing Sensitivity**\n",
    "- Customers with higher monthly charges are more likely to churn  \n",
    "- Price-value perception plays a key role in retention  \n",
    "\n",
