    "- Customers using additional services (TechSupport, OnlineSecurity, etc.) are less likely to churn  \n",
    "- Higher service integration increases switching cost and loyalty  \n",
    "\n",
    " **Contract Structure Impact**\n",
    "- Month-to-month contracts have the highest churn rates  \n",
    "- Long-term contracts significantly reduce churn  \n",
    "- Commitment level is a major retention driver  \n",
    "\n",
    " **Customer Behavior Segmentation**\n",
